ang tiwala at promosyon ni Mr. Wang.

00:14:33.200 --> 00:14:34.144
Mr. Wang,

00:14:35.160 --> 00:14:36.360
totoo ba ito?

00:14:36.680 --> 00:14:39.800
Your Honor,
huwag kang makinig sa kanyang one-sided claims!

00:14:39.920 --> 00:14:41.000
Siya...

00:14:41.000 --> 00:14:41.880
Qin Si...

00:14:42.200 --> 00:14:43.640
Nabaliw na siya! Nakakabaliw siya!

00:14:43.640 --> 00:14:44.600
baliw ako?

00:14:44.600 --> 00:14:45.568
Qin Si.

00:14:46.120 --> 00:14:49.480
Paulit-ulit mong sinasabi
na lahat ng ginawa mo

00:14:49.480 --> 00:14:51.360
ay nasa ilalim ng utos ni Mr. Wang.

00:14:52.440 --> 00:14:53.520
May ebidensya ka ba?

00:14:56.880 --> 00:14:57.920
Walang ebidensya.

00:14:59.280 --> 00:15:00.720
Kung walang ebidensya,

00:15:00.920 --> 00:15:02.800
how dare you frame me?

00:15:03.320 --> 00:15:04.520
Paano katawa-tawa.

00:15:05.200 --> 00:15:08.280
Ang isang taksil na alipin
na tulad mo ay nararapat na parusahan!

00:15:09.440 --> 00:15:10.440
Walang utang na loob na kawawa!

00:15:10.520 --> 00:15:12.800
Kahit sa pintuan ng kamatayan,
gumagawa ka ng maling paratang!

00:15:13.664 --> 00:15:14.520
honey,

00:15:15.120 --> 00:15:16.240
parang tayo talaga

00:15:16.240 --> 00:15:17.560
nagkasala kay Mr. Wang.

00:15:17.800 --> 00:15:19.280
Qin Si

00:15:19.600 --> 00:15:21.240
wala talagang ebidensya.

00:15:23.360 --> 00:15:24.280
sinta,

00:15:24.280 --> 00:15:27.520
kung si Qin Si ay tunay na
kumpidensyal na lingkod ni Wang,

00:15:28.360 --> 00:15:30.560
hindi ba niya malalaman ang marami sa kanilang mga sikreto?

00:15:32.544 --> 00:15:33.696
Tama!

00:15:33.696 --> 00:15:34.840
Your Honor.

00:15:35.200 --> 00:15:36.280
Alam ko talaga

00:15:36.280 --> 00:15:37.480
isang sikreto ng pamilya Wang.

00:15:38.040 --> 00:15:38.880
Sabihin mo.

00:15:39.960 --> 00:15:41.400
Tumaas ang benta ng boss ko

00:15:41.760 --> 00:15:44.040
sa pamamagitan ng pag-order sa mga babae
sa Tianxiang Tea House

00:15:44.160 --> 00:15:45.520
para magdagdag ng insenso at anesthetics

00:15:45.640 --> 00:15:47.200
sa tsaa ng mga customer.

00:15:47.400 --> 00:15:48.840
Dahil dito, nataranta ang mga customer

00:15:48.840 --> 00:15:49.888
at gumastos ng mas maraming pera.

00:15:49.960 --> 00:15:51.360
Ngunit matagal na paggamit

00:15:51.680 --> 00:15:53.320
ng insenso at anesthetics

00:15:53.440 --> 00:15:54.960
nagdudulot ng pisikal na pinsala

00:15:55.200 --> 00:15:56.600
at kayang pumatay ng tao!

00:15:56.600 --> 00:15:57.600
Mr. Wang,

00:15:57.600 --> 00:15:58.560
totoo ba ito?

00:15:59.840 --> 00:16:01.320
Syempre hindi!

00:16:01.560 --> 00:16:04.040
Nagsasagawa ako ng negosyo nang marangal.

00:16:04.080 --> 00:16:06.400
Hindi ako gagamit ng gayong kasuklam-suklam na pamamaraan!

00:16:07.040 --> 00:16:07.920
Mga salitang walang basehan.

00:16:08.200 --> 00:16:09.840
Qin Si, may ebidensya ka ba?

00:16:12.080 --> 00:16:14.080
Ang mga babaeng iyon ay binili ni Mr. Wang.

00:16:14.560 --> 00:16:16.320
How dare they show evidence?

00:16:17.520 --> 00:16:19.120
Kung walang ebidensya,

00:16:19.200 --> 00:16:20.800
sinusubukan mo pa ba akong i-frame?

00:16:21.400 --> 00:16:23.480
Ngayon, gusto kong malaman

00:16:24.760 --> 00:16:26.840
sinong nag-utos sayo na i-frame ako!

00:16:27.400 --> 00:16:28.560
Maaari akong magpatotoo.

00:16:38.320 --> 00:16:39.280
Your Honor.

00:16:39.640 --> 00:16:42.320
Isa akong hostess sa Tianxiang Tea House

00:16:42.600 --> 00:16:43.560
pinangalanang Niaoniao.

00:16:43.560 --> 00:16:44.720
kaya kong patunayan

00:16:44.720 --> 00:16:46.720
totoo ang sinabi ni Qin Si.

00:16:47.000 --> 00:16:48.480
Pinilit nga kami ni Mr. Wang

00:16:48.480 --> 00:16:50.280
sa mga customer ng droga.

00:16:50.720 --> 00:16:51.880
Kung hindi ka naniniwala sa akin,

00:16:51.920 --> 00:16:53.640
maaari kang maghanap sa bahay ng tsaa.

00:16:53.920 --> 00:16:55.480
Sa ilalim ng dressing table ng bawat babae,

00:16:55.480 --> 00:16:56.600
may nakatagong drawer.

00:16:57.120 --> 00:16:58.600
Malalaman mo kung totoo ito

00:16:58.720 --> 00:17:00.000
pagkatapos maghanap.

00:17:03.920 --> 00:17:06.320
Dahil mayroon tayong
mga saksi at ebidensya,

00:17:06.880 --> 00:17:09.040
ikulong sina G. Wang at Qin Si

00:17:09.040 --> 00:17:10.280
at ilagay muna sila sa kulungan.

00:17:10.640 --> 00:17:13.480
Hanapin agad ang Tianxiang Tea House.

